{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">通过探究</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，提高设计实验的能力，并通过比较不同物质的吸热能力，知道不同物质的比热容一</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">般</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">不同</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"原理","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">不同物质比热容一般不同。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"器材","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">质量相等</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">水和</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">食用油、</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">相同规格</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">2<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个酒精灯</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">2<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">支</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">温度计</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">秒表</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、火柴</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"步骤","data":"<p style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">1.提出问题</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">：不同物质在质量和升高的温度都相同的情况下，吸</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">收</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的热量是否相同？</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">2.猜想</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">和假设：等质量的不同物质在升高</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">相同</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">温度时，吸收的热量是</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">______<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">3.设计实验</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">和进行实验</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">：</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（</span>1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）用温度计</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">测量水和食用油的初始温度，并记录在表格中。</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（</span>2<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）用相同规格</span></spa