style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吸收</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">热量</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">______<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">其中</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">______<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吸收</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">本领要强得多。</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（</span>2<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）在物理学中，</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">将一定质量的某种物质，在温度升高时吸收的</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">______<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">与</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">它的质量和升高的温度</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的</span>______<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">之比</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，叫做这种物质的</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">______<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"结论","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">1.相等质量的水和食用油，在升高</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">相同温度的</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">情况下</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吸收</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">热量</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">不同，</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">其中</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">水吸收热量的</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">本领要强得多。</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">2.在物理学中，</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">将一定质量的某种物质，在温度升高时吸收的</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">热量与</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">它的质量和升高的温度</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的乘积之比</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，叫做这种物质的</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">比热容。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"补充","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">水的比热容较大，可以用来做发动机冷却剂或暖气的介质。</span></span></span></span></p>"}],"x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":600}